I can't.

00:07:38.210 --> 00:07:39.670
Why not?

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:42.540
Precisely because we're in the same profession.

00:07:46.380 --> 00:07:50.420
Shirasaki has his own work to focus on.

00:07:52.290 --> 00:07:53.460
Shirasaki.

00:07:53.580 --> 00:07:54.250
Yes?

00:07:54.380 --> 00:07:55.330
You need to show more.

00:07:55.460 --> 00:07:57.790
Until his big play is over,

00:07:58.500 --> 00:08:01.380
I don't want to burden him with my problems.

00:08:25.210 --> 00:08:26.830
Welcome home.

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:30.250
I'm home.

00:08:55.250 --> 00:08:57.630
The smell of Asami-san...

00:09:00.790 --> 00:09:02.790
It really is calming.

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:09.130
It feels like it's been a while...

00:09:10.330 --> 00:09:12.420
since we've been able to see each other like this.

00:09:14.130 --> 00:09:15.080
Yeah.

00:09:20.250 --> 00:09:21.460
This is nice.

00:09:22.830 --> 00:09:25.210
I love your curry, Asami-san.

00:09:28.210 --> 00:09:29.420
Thanks.

00:09:30.290 --> 00:09:31.710
I'm gonna go wash my hands.

00:09:31.830 --> 00:09:33.290
Okay.

