By the way...

00:09:52.710 --> 00:09:55.130
When does the film in the UK start shooting?

00:09:58.790 --> 00:10:01.630
There's an eight-hour time difference.

00:10:02.540 --> 00:10:08.080
Guess it'll be hard to find time to call each other.

00:10:13.330 --> 00:10:14.880
I might not take the role.

00:10:16.710 --> 00:10:18.000
Huh?

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:25.380
I don't think I can do a good job.

00:10:30.540 --> 00:10:32.000
Right now...

00:10:33.460 --> 00:10:36.080
my current shoot isn't going well.

00:10:39.290 --> 00:10:42.130
Whenever I have a scene with my mother,

00:10:43.500 --> 00:10:46.380
I can't help but think of my own mom,

00:10:47.290 --> 00:10:49.210
and I just can't get it right.

00:10:57.330 --> 00:10:59.750
I read my dad's novel.

00:11:00.210 --> 00:11:02.080
The main character...

00:11:02.210 --> 00:11:04.170
is just like him.

00:11:10.460 --> 00:11:12.880
If I take the offer,

00:11:13.670 --> 00:11:15.920
it would mean playing that man.

00:11:21.750 --> 00:11:24.210
I'm already struggling as it is.

00:11:24.880 --> 00:11:27.920
The thought of playing him...

00:11:37.420 --> 00:11:39.130
Are you going to turn it down?

00:11:47.170 --> 00:11:48.580
Maybe.

00:11:51.880 --> 00:11:53.500
You're feeling anxious, aren't you?

00:12:13.830 --> 00:12:15.170
Me too...

00:12:18.080 --> 00:12:20.040
I've been so anxious.

00:12:24.710 --> 00:12:26.250
Asami-san.

00:12:28.290 --> 00:12:31.460
You're always so many steps ahead of me.

00:12:33.580 --> 00:12:38.460
I try so hard to catch up, but I never can.

00:12:48.460 --> 00:12:49.830
When will I ever...

00:12:51.670 --> 00:12:55.080
be able to stand beside you as an equal?

00:12:58.040 --> 00:13:01.710
Will that day ever come?

00:13:03.210 --> 00:13:06.830
What if the play bombs tomorrow,

00:13:06.960 --> 00:13:09.380
and I never get another offer?

00:13:09.500 --> 00:13:12.130
You're always moving forward, Asami-san.

00:13:12.250 --> 00:13:15.960
What will I do if you leave me behind again?

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:17.460
That's not going to happen.

00:13:17.580 --> 00:13:19.460
How can you be so sure?

00:13:20.130 --> 00:13:21.460
Because...

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:25.290
You just got an amazing offer,
didn't you, Asami-san?

00:13:26.630 --> 00:13:29.330
A movie at an international studio.

00:13:30.420 --> 00:13:34.080
That's a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity,
no matter how much you want it.

00:13:34.500 --> 00:13:36.920
It's such a great thing,

00:13:38.630 --> 00:13:40.580
and you're going to turn it down?

00:13:46.710 --> 00:13:51.670
My mother probably wouldn't want me
to be in my father's movie anyway.

00:13:51.790 --> 00:13:54.250
But what do you want, Asami-san?

00:13:58.170 --> 00:14:01.750
If you really don't want to do it,

00:14:01.880 --> 00:14:03.920
then that's fine.

00:14:04.040 --> 00:14:06.380
But I can't help feeling that right now,

00:14:08.580 --> 00:14:11.540
you're just making excuses not to do it.

00:14:13.170 --> 00:14:15.170
That's not true.

00:14:15.290 --> 00:14:16.880
I've been...

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:19.210
